        <h1>Rails Girls Galway
            <small>20-21st June 2014</small>
        </h1>
        <h3>Hi Girls :)<br /> Let's learn together how to make new things with the Web!</h3>
        <p>Rails Girls comes to Galway again!
            During the *free* two-days workshop in June 2014, we will dive into the magical world of Ruby on Rails and build an application together, from scratch. </p>
        <p>
<a href="https://iammyr.wufoo.com/forms/rails-girls-galway-2014-application/" target="_blank">
Applications are now opened!</a><br /> 
Places are limited so be sure to <a href="https://iammyr.wufoo.com/forms/rails-girls-galway-2014-application/" target="_blank"><strong>submit your interest</strong></a> <br />
<strong><a href="https://iammyr.wufoo.com/forms/rails-girls-galway-2014-application/">Applications</a> close:</strong> <del>June 5th</del> - <strong>Extended till June 13th</strong><br/>
                <strong>Acceptances informed:</strong> June 8th

</p>


 

